history.content:
Dear Students,

Tomorrow, Wednesday, December 12 will be the last CS drop-in advising hours of this semester. Advisors will be available this Wed, 10-12PM & 1-4PM in 315 & 379 Soda.
Appointments are available via CalCentral through this Friday, December 14. 
CS advising appointments will not be available December 17,2018 through January 4, 2019. Advisors will still be responding to emails sent to cs-advising@cs.berkeley.edu during this time, so please send questions to this alias.
Best wishes for finals! You can do it!
CS Advising
